mp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-30m.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-30m.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-30m.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-30m.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-30m.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-30m.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A thank you message from FromSoftware for 30 million sales of Elden Ring.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-30m.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-30m.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                        \u003cfigcaption\u003eFromSoftware\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n                        \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e has officially reached a new milestone: \u003cstrong\u003e30 million units sold\u003c/strong\u003e. This follows FromSoftware and Bandai Namco\u0026#39;s \u003ca href=\"https://www.fromsoftware.jp/jp/pressrelease_detail.html?tgt=20241213_eldenring_nightreign_debut\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eprevious update\u003c/a\u003e of 28.6 million copies. Notably, this figure does not include sales of the \u003ca href=\"https://gamerant.com/tag/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eShadow of the Erdtree\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e expansion, which performed well in its own right—selling over five million copies in just three days.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe game sold 20 million units within its first year after launching in February 2022. So while an additional 10 million over the past two years isn\u0026#39;t a dramatic leap, it reinforces the franchise\u0026#39;s staying power—and puts \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e among the most successful titles of all time.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eWith 30 million units sold, \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e now sits above \u003ca href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/super-mario-odyssey/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eSuper Mario Odyssey\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, right alongside \u003cem\u003eCyberpunk 2077\u003c/em\u003e and \u003cem\u003eBlack Myth: Wukong\u003c/em\u003e, and just below \u003cem\u003eHogwarts Legacy\u003c/em\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/the-legend-of-zelda-breath-of-the-wild/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eThe Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, and Bandai Namco\u0026#39;s own \u003cem\u003eSuper Smash Bros. Ultimate\u003c/em\u003e. It\u0026#39;s still a ways off from catching \u003cem\u003eMinecraft\u003c/em\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/this-is-the-best-selling-game-in-history/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ethe best-selling game ever\u003c/a\u003e, but the list of titles ahead is growing shorter.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"the-elden-ring-effect\"\u003e\n                        \u003cstrong\u003eThe Elden Ring Effect\u003c/strong\u003e\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u0026#39;s\u003c/em\u003e monumental success has had a trickle-down effect across FromSoftware\u0026#39;s other properties—especially the \u003ca href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/dark-souls/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eDark Souls\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e series. Prior to \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u0026#39;s\u003c/em\u003e release, the entire \u003cem\u003eDark Souls\u003c/em\u003e trilogy had \u003cem\u003eonly \u003c/em\u003esold a combined 27 million units. But after \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e hit the market, sales of the \u003cem\u003eDark Souls\u003c/em\u003e games \u003cstrong\u003esurged to a combined 35 million units\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eFollowing the mainstream breakthrough of \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e, newcomers to the soulslike genre flocked to explore its predecessors.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"fromsoftware-isn-39-t-done-with-the-lands-between\"\u003e\n                        \u003cstrong\u003eFromSoftware Isn\u0026#39;t Done With the Lands Between\u003c/strong\u003e\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-nightreign-1.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;FromSoftware\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-nightreign-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-nightreign-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-nightreign-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-nightreign-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-nightreign-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-nightreign-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-nightreign-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-nightreign-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"3840\" height=\"2160\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A player dropping into a match of Elden Ring Nightreign\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-nightreign-1.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/elden-ring-nightreign-1.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                        \u003cfigcaption\u003eFromSoftware\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n                        \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e With momentum like this, it\u0026#39;s clear \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u0026#39;s\u003c/em\u003e journey is far from over. \u003ca href=\"https://screenrant.com/elden-ring-2-not-in-production-fromsoftware-op-ed/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eWhile a direct sequel is reportedly not yet in development\u003c/a\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003eElden Ring: Nightreign\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e—a spin-off, battle royale-inspired adventure set in the same universe—is scheduled to launch on \u003cstrong\u003eMay 30, 2025\u003c/strong\u003e. Much like \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e boosted interest in the \u003cem\u003eDark Souls\u003c/em\u003e trilogy, \u003cem\u003eNightreign \u003c/em\u003ewill likely serve as a gateway for multiplayer-first players to finally try \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIn addition, \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e is coming to the \u003ca href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/nintendo-switch-2/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eNintendo Switch 2\u003c/a\u003e. The original Switch never saw a release, so whether it\u0026#39;s new players diving in for the first time or longtime fans picking up a second copy for portable play, the 30 million units sold milestone is unlikely to be the game\u0026#39;s final tally.\u003c/p\u003e    \n    \n    \n                \n                                \n                    \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n                    \n                \n                                            \n    \n        \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/sharedimages/2024/12/mixcollage-08-dec-2024-02-50-pm-6945-1.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\" data-show-streamrentbuy-links=\"false\" data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"faba-4f62-bca4597c43ec\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                               